  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK367">
<l>avāviṉai yāṟṟa vaṟuppiṟ ṟavāviṉai </l>
<l>tāṉvēṇṭu māṟṟāṉ varum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If a man thoroughly cut off all desire, the deeds, which confer immortality, will come to him, in the path in which he seeks them.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
